(97, 27, 'wpsm_faq_data', 's:2012:"a:6:{i:0;a:4:{s:9:"faq_title";s:41:"How competitive are your trade-in prices?";s:14:"faq_title_icon";s:9:"fa-laptop";s:18:"enable_single_icon";s:2:"no";s:8:"faq_desc";s:216:"We constantly monitor the pre-owned prices of cars (via many platforms such as popular websites and classifieds) as well as prevailing market conditions. This enables us to offer very competitive prices for your car.";}i:1;a:4:{s:9:"faq_title";s:23:"Is your COE guaranteed?";s:14:"faq_title_icon";s:9:"fa-laptop";s:18:"enable_single_icon";s:3:"yes";s:8:"faq_desc";s:121:"Yes, our COE package is guaranteed. If the COE prices increase, we will offer a commensurately higher COE rebate package.";}i:2;a:4:{s:9:"faq_title";s:41:"How are your stocks of vehicles for sale?";s:14:"faq_title_icon";s:9:"fa-laptop";s:18:"enable_single_icon";s:3:"yes";s:8:"faq_desc";s:215:"We endeavor to maintain a healthy inventory that comprises over 100 different makes and models of cars. And this inventory is replenished on a bi-monthly basis. We are also able to offer for sale, the latest models.";}i:3;a:4:{s:9:"faq_title";s:70:"What will happen to my deposit if my loan application is not approved?";s:14:"faq_title_icon";s:9:"fa-laptop";s:18:"enable_single_icon";s:3:"yes";s:8:"faq_desc";s:134:"If it is not approved, we will refund the full deposit to you. Alternatively, you can look at other financing options such as leasing.";}i:4;a:4:{s:9:"faq_title";s:46:"What kind of after-sales service do you offer?";s:14:"faq_title_icon";s:9:"fa-laptop";s:18:"enable_single_icon";s:3:"yes";s:8:"faq_desc";s:131:"We partner one of Singapore’s most reputable and well-equipped workshops to handle all servicing, maintenance and repair matters.";}i:5;a:4:{s:9:"faq_title";s:71:"Why is your pricing generally lower than that of the authorized agents?";s:14:"faq_title_icon";s:9:"fa-laptop";s:18:"enable_single_icon";s:3:"yes";s:8:"faq_desc";s:106:"We have lower overheads (operating costs), hence we are able to offer our cars at more competitive prices.";}}";'),
