(18, 1, '2016-05-22 02:50:43', '2016-05-22 02:50:43', '<div class="container medium-container">\r\n<div class="row">\r\n<div class="rental col-md-12 col-xs-12" style="text-align: left;">An agreement is made between Vin''s Car Rental Pte Ltd of Blk 12 Sin Ming Road #01-67 Singapore 575656 (hereinafter called "the Owner") and the person whose particulars and signature appear overleaf (hereinafter called "the Hirer"). The Owner HEREBY rents to the Hirer and the Hirer takes the motor vehicle described overleaf (hereinafter called "the Vehicle") subject to all terms, conditions and stipulation of this Agreement, in connection whereof the Hirer acknowledges and agrees as follows:-</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="row">\r\n<div class="rental col-md-12 col-xs-12">\r\n<div class="para"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-54" src="http://vinsmotor-webinno.stag-innov8te.com//wp-content/uploads/2016/05/policy.png" alt="policy" width="24" height="20" /></div>\r\n<div class="policy-txt">1. Only the Hirer/Driver is allowed to drive the vehicle. For additional drivers, additional charges may apply.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="row">\r\n<div class="rental col-md-12 col-xs-12">\r\n<div class="para"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-54" src="http://vinsmotor-webinno.stag-innov8te.com//wp-content/uploads/2016/05/policy.png" alt="policy" width="24" height="20" /></div>\r\n<div class="policy-txt">2. Hirer is liable for all parking fines and traffic violations.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="row">\r\n<div class="rental col-md-12 col-xs-12">\r\n<div class="para"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-54" src="http://vinsmotor-webinno.stag-innov8te.com//wp-content/uploads/2016/05/policy.png" alt="policy" width="24" height="20" /></div>\r\n<div class="policy-txt">3. This vehicle can only be used within Singapore only. For Hirers who wish to enter Malaysia, an additional fee of $30.00 per entry is chargeable for additional insurance. Failure to inform the Owner before entering Malaysia will result in a $50.00 fine.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="row">\r\n<div class="rental col-md-12 col-xs-12">\r\n<div class="para"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-54" src="http://vinsmotor-webinno.stag-innov8te.com//wp-content/uploads/2016/05/policy.png" alt="policy" width="24" height="20" /></div>\r\n<div class="policy-txt">4. Excess – Hirer is liable to pay up to $2,000 for repairs in the case of an accident within Singapore, plus rental while damaged vehicle is under repair. For young drivers (aged 22 to 26), the excess payable is $2,500. For accidents in Malaysia, excess payable is $5,000.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="row">\r\n<div class="rental col-md-12 col-xs-12">\r\n<div class="para"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-54" src="http://vinsmotor-webinno.stag-innov8te.com//wp-content/uploads/2016/05/policy.png" alt="policy" width="24" height="20" /></div>\r\n<div class="policy-txt">5.Smoking in the vehicle is strictly prohibited. At the Owner’s discretion, Hirer is liable to pay $300.00 as cleaning fees if he/she smokes in the vehicle.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="row">\r\n<div class="rental col-md-12 col-xs-12">\r\n<div class="para"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-54" src="http://vinsmotor-webinno.stag-innov8te.com//wp-content/uploads/2016/05/policy.png" alt="policy" width="24" height="20" /></div>\r\n<div class="policy-txt">6.And many more.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="row">\r\n<div class="rental col-md-12 col-xs-12" style="text-align: left;">The above points are but a list of the key terms &amp; conditions of our rental agreement and is not a full representation of the of our rental agreement. \r\n\r\nFor the full list of our terms and conditions, please refer to the back page of our actual rental agreement.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="row"></div>\r\n<div class="row"></div>', 'Rental Policy', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'rental-policy', 