(29, 1, '2016-10-18 02:05:44', '2016-10-18 02:05:44', '<div class="container medium-container">\n<div class="row">\n<div class="faqs col-md-12 col-xs-12">\n<div class="ques"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-44" src="http://vinsmotor-webinno.stag-innov8te.com//wp-content/uploads/2016/05/faq.png" alt="faq" width="30" height="30" /><strong style="font-size: 18px; margin-left: 14px;">What are your collection and return time for your rental cars?</strong></div>\n<div class="ans">Collection time is anywhere from 9.30AM in the morning to 5.30PM in the evening.</div>\n<div class="ans">As we calculate our daily rental by the 24-hour system, your return timing will be the same time as which you collected the vehicle.</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="row">\n<div class="faqs col-md-12 col-xs-12">\n<div class="ques"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-44" src="http://vinsmotor-webinno.stag-innov8te.com//wp-content/uploads/2016/05/faq.png" alt="faq" width="30" height="30" /><strong style="font-size: 18px; margin-left: 14px;">What if I return the car late?</strong></div>\n<div class="ans">We usually give our clients about 1-2 hours leeway when it comes to returning. However, any later than that, we will charge a min. of half day rental if the vehicle is returned to us in the same day. For any later than a day, daily rates will apply.</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="row">\n<div class="faqs col-md-12 col-xs-12">\n<div class="ques"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-44" src="http://vinsmotor-webinno.stag-innov8te.com//wp-content/uploads/2016/05/faq.png" alt="faq" width="30" height="30" /><strong style="font-size: 18px; margin-left: 14px;">Can I smoke inside the car?</strong></div>\n<div class="ans">We regret to inform you that all of our vehicles are non-smoking vehicles. Should the Hirer be found smoking in the vehicle, he/she will be liable to pay up to $300 in cleaning fees.</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="row">\n<div class="faqs col-md-12 col-xs-12">\n<div class="ques"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-44" src="http://vinsmotor-webinno.stag-innov8te.com//wp-content/uploads/2016/05/faq.png" alt="faq" width="30" height="30" /><strong style="font-size: 18px; margin-left: 14px;">Does the car come with petrol?</strong></div>\n<div class="ans">Yes and No. We do not practice the full tank policy, as such you will only be required to return us the vehicle with the same amount of fuel as when you took the vehicle. If the return level is lower than the collection level, we will charge a pro-rated amount for the difference. However, please note that if you return the car with more fuel, we will be unable to refund you the difference.</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="row">\n<div class="faqs col-md-12 col-xs-12">\n<div class="ques"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-44" src="http://vinsmotor-webinno.stag-innov8te.com//wp-content/uploads/2016/05/faq.png" alt="faq" width="30" height="30" /><strong style="font-size: 18px; margin-left: 14px;">Can I go to Malaysia with the car? </strong></div>\n<div class="ans">For entry into Malaysia, there will be additional charges. Please check with our staff with regards to the pricing.\nShould the Hirer be caught entering Malaysia without informing us, there will be a $50 penalty imposed on the Hirer.</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="row">\n<div class="faqs col-md-12 col-xs-12">\n<div class="ques"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-44" src="http://vinsmotor-webinno.stag-innov8te.com//wp-content/uploads/2016/05/faq.png" alt="faq" width="30" height="30" /><strong style="font-size: 18px; margin-left: 14px;">What should I do if the car breaks down? </strong></div>\n<div class="ans">Please give us a call at 64532121 during office hours, or 64581111 if it is after office hours. We will send our emergency breakdown team to attend to you in the quickest time.</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="row">\n<div class="faqs col-md-12 col-xs-12">\n<div class="ques"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-44" src="http://vinsmotor-webinno.stag-innov8te.com//wp-content/uploads/2016/05/faq.png" alt="faq" width="30" height="30" /><strong style="font-size: 18px; margin-left: 14px;">What should I do if I get into an accident?</strong></div>\n<div class="ans">First of all, make sure that there are no injuries to any parties. Next, exchange particulars with the other party, and snap as many photos as possible. The cars involved in the accident, the location, the other parties'' IC &amp; driving license etc. Next, give us a call and we will advise you where to go from there.</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'FAQs', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '7-autosave-v1', '', '', '2016-10-18 02:05:44', '2016-10-18 02:05:44', '', 7, 'http://vinsmotor-webinno.stag-innov8te.com//2016/05/22/7-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(30, 1, '2016-05-22 04:54:16', '2016-05-22 04:54:16', 'How competitive are your trade-in prices?\r\nWe constantly monitor the pre-owned prices of cars (via many platforms such as popular websites and classifieds) as well as prevailing market conditions. This enables us to offer very competitive prices for your car.\r\nIs your COE guaranteed?\r\nYes, our COE package is guaranteed. If the COE prices increase, we will offer a commensurately higher COE rebate package.\r\nHow are your stocks of vehicles for sale?\r\nWe endeavor to maintain a healthy inventory that comprises over 100 different makes and models of cars. And this inventory is replenished on a bi-monthly basis. We are also able to offer for sale, the latest models.\r\nWhat will happen to my deposit if my loan application is not approved?\r\nIf it is not approved, we will refund the full deposit to you. Alternatively, you can look at other financing options such as leasing.\r\nWhat kind of after-sales service do you offer?\r\nWe partner one of Singapore’s most reputable and well-equipped workshops to handle all servicing, maintenance and repair matters.\r\nWhy is your pricing generally lower than that of the authorized agents?\r\nWe have lower overheads (operating costs), hence we are able to offer our cars at more competitive prices.', 'FAQs', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '7-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-05-22 04:54:16', '2016-05-22 04:54:16', '', 7, 'http://vinsmotor-webinno.stag-innov8te.com//2016/05/22/7-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(32, 1, '2016-05-22 05:48:59', '2016-05-22 05:48:59', '<div class="container">\r\n    <div class="row">\r\n	 <div class="col-md-2 col-xs-12">\r\n                  <img src="http://vinsmotor-webinno.stag-innov8te.com//wp-content/uploads/2016/05/faq.png" alt="faq" width="39" height="39" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-31" />\r\n         </div>\r\n <div class="col-md-10 col-xs-12">\r\nHow competitive are your trade-in prices?\r\nWe constantly monitor the pre-owned prices of cars (via many platforms such as popular websites and classifieds) as well as prevailing market conditions. This enables us to offer very competitive prices for your car.\r\n</div>\r\n <div class="col-md-10 col-xs-12">\r\nIs your COE guaranteed?\r\nYes, our COE package is guaranteed. If the COE prices increase, we will offer a commensurately higher COE rebate package.\r\n</div>\r\n <div class="col-md-10 col-xs-12">\r\nHow are your stocks of vehicles for sale?\r\nWe endeavor to maintain a healthy inventory that comprises over 100 different makes and models of cars. And this inventory is replenished on a bi-monthly basis. We are also able to offer for sale, the latest models.\r\n</div>\r\n <div class="col-md-10 col-xs-12">\r\nWhat will happen to my deposit if my loan application is not approved?\r\nIf it is not approved, we will refund the full deposit to you. Alternatively, you can look at other financing options such as leasing.\r\n</div>\r\n <div class="col-md-10 col-xs-12">\r\nWhat kind of after-sales service do you offer?\r\nWe partner one of Singapore’s most reputable and well-equipped workshops to handle all servicing, maintenance and repair matters.\r\n</div>\r\n <div class="col-md-10 col-xs-12">\r\nWhy is your pricing generally lower than that of the authorized agents?\r\nWe have lower overheads (operating costs), hence we are able to offer our cars at more competitive prices.\r\n</div>', 'FAQs', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '7-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-05-22 05:48:59', '2016-