(323, 1, '2016-07-08 07:02:13', '2016-07-08 07:02:13', '<div class="container medium-container">\r\n<div class="row">\r\n<div class="faqs col-md-12 col-xs-12">\r\n<div class="ques"><img src="http://vinsmotor-webinno.stag-innov8te.com//wp-content/uploads/2016/05/faq.png" alt="faq" width="30" height="30" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-44" /><strong style="font-size:18px;    margin-left: 14px;">How competitive are your trade-in prices?</strong></div>\r\n<div class="ans">We constantly monitor the pre-owned prices of cars (via many platforms such as popular websites and classifieds) as well as prevailing market conditions. This enables us to offer very competitive prices for your car.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="row">\r\n<div class="faqs col-md-12 col-xs-12">\r\n<div class="ques"><img src="http://vinsmotor-webinno.stag-innov8te.com//wp-content/uploads/2016/05/faq.png" alt="faq" width="30" height="30" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-44" /><strong style="font-size:18px;    margin-left: 14px;">Is your COE guaranteed?</strong></div>\r\n<div class="ans">Yes, our COE package is guaranteed. If the COE prices increase, we will offer a commensurately higher COE rebate package.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="row">\r\n<div class="faqs col-md-12 col-xs-12">\r\n<div class="ques"><img src="http://vinsmotor-webinno.stag-innov8te.com//wp-content/uploads/2016/05/faq.png" alt="faq" width="30" height="30" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-44" /><strong style="font-size:18px;margin-left: 14px;">How are your stocks of vehicles for sale?</strong></div>\r\n<div class="ans">We endeavor to maintain a healthy inventory that comprises over 100 different makes and models of cars. And this inventory is replenished on a bi-monthly basis. We are also able to offer for sale, the latest models.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="row">\r\n<div class="faqs col-md-12 col-xs-12">\r\n<div class="ques"><img src="http://vinsmotor-webinno.stag-innov8te.com//wp-content/uploads/2016/05/faq.png" alt="faq" width="30" height="30" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-44" /><strong style="font-size:18px;margin-left: 14px;">What will happen to my deposit if my loan application is not approved?</strong></div>\r\n<div class="ans">If it is not approved, we will refund the full deposit to you. Alternatively, you can look at other financing options such as leasing.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="row">\r\n<div class="faqs col-md-12 col-xs-12">\r\n<div class="ques"><img src="http://vinsmotor-webinno.stag-innov8te.com//wp-content/uploads/2016/05/faq.png" alt="faq" width="30" height="30" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-44" /><strong style="font-size:18px;margin-left: 14px;">What kind of after-sales service do you offer?</strong></div>\r\n<div class="ans">We partner one of Singapore’s most reputable and well-equipped workshops to handle all servicing, maintenance and repair matters.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="row">\r\n<div class="faqs col-md-12 col-xs-12">\r\n<div class="ques"><img src="http://vinsmotor-webinno.stag-innov8te.com//wp-content/uploads/2016/05/faq.png" alt="faq" width="30" height="30" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-44" /><strong style="font-size:18px;margin-left: 14px;">Why is your pricing generally lower than that of the authorized agents?</strong></div>\r\n<div class="ans">We have lower overheads (operating costs), hence we are able to offer our cars at more competitive prices.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'FAQs', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '7-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-07-08 07:02:13', '2016-07-08 07:02:13', '', 7, 'http://vinsmotor-webinno.stag-innov8te.com/?p=323', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
