o make payment of the rental in advance as provided in the above Clause 10a or 10b; or where the Owner in his discretion extend the hire period without the Hirer paying the full rental in advance as provided in Clause 10a or 10b, whichever is applicable, then without prejudice to other rights of the Owner, the Hirer shall be liable to pay the Owner rental calculated on a daily basis rate and the rate chargeable shall be as stipulated overleaf. In addition, the Owner may, at his discretion, choose to make a demand  under Clause 1 to repossess the vehicle. The Owner will not be liable for any damages and the Hirer will be liable for all costs and expenses incurred, as stipulated under Clauses 2-4. Further to that, the Owner may choose to terminate the existing rental agreement and the security deposit will not be refunded to the Hirer.</div>\r\n<div class="container medium-container">\r\n<div class="row">\r\n<div class="policy-txt"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-54" src="http://vinsmotor-webinno.stag-innov8te.com//wp-content/uploads/2016/05/policy.png" alt="policy" width="24" height="20" /></div>\r\n<div class="policy-txt"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-54" src="http://vinsmotor-webinno.stag-innov8te.com//wp-content/uploads/2016/05/policy.png" alt="policy" width="24" height="20" /></div>\r\n<div class="policy-txt"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-54" src="http://vinsmotor-webinno.stag-innov8te.com//wp-content/uploads/2016/05/policy.png" alt="policy" width="24" height="20" /></div>\r\n<div class="policy-txt"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-54" src="http://vinsmotor-webinno.stag-innov8te.com//wp-content/uploads/2016/05/policy.png" alt="policy" width="24" height="20" /></div>\r\n<div class="policy-txt"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-54" src="http://vinsmotor-webinno.stag-innov8te.com//wp-content/uploads/2016/05/policy.png" alt="policy" width="24" height="20" /></div>\r\n<div class="policy-txt"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-54" src="http://vinsmotor-webinno.stag-innov8te.com//wp-content/uploads/2016/05/policy.png" alt="policy" width="24" height="20" /></div>\r\n<div class="policy-txt">27. Any provision of this Agreement or any part of any Clause thereof which is prohibited or unenforceable in a Court of law shall be ineffective only to the extent of such prohibition or unenforceability shall invalidate or affect the remaining provisions of this Agreement or the remaining parts of the Clause affected.</div>\r\n<div class="policy-txt"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-54" src="http://vinsmotor-webinno.stag-innov8te.com//wp-content/uploads/2016/05/policy.png" alt="policy" width="24" height="20" /></div>\r\n<div class="policy-txt"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-54" src="http://vinsmotor-webinno.stag-innov8te.com//wp-content/uploads/2016/05/policy.png" alt="policy" width="24" height="20" /></div>\r\n<div class="policy-txt"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'Rental Policy', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '18-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-07-23 06:55:29', '2016-07-23 06:55:29', '', 18, 'http://vinsmotor-webinno.stag-innov8te.com/?p=358', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
