(781, 1, '2016-10-24 10:04:01', '2016-10-24 10:04:01', '<h4 class="container medium-container">Vin''s Car Rental Pte Ltd (previously known as K &amp; V Car Rental Pte Ltd), was established in 1992 as a Car Rental &amp; Leasing company, providing affordable and competitive rates for car hire in Singapore.</h4>\r\n<div class="container medium-container">Since our establishment, we have proven to be a reliable car rental company, offering personalized services to all our customers. We have vehicles available for short term rentals, long term rentals, renting for Uber/Grab, as well as both used/new vehicles available for long term leasing. All our cars are properly groomed and maintained, and we practice a no holds barred policy in servicing and maintaining our fleet. We stand firm by our belief that the lifeblood to any business lies in being able to deliver customer service excellence.Besides that, Vin''s Car Rental is also part of the Vin''s Automotive Group of companies, which includes our Motor Workshop arm, as well as our New Parallal Import Cars arm. As such, we are able to provide a one stop service for all our customers. Do check out our other services provided by clicking on the menu below.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="container medium-container">\r\n\r\n<img class="img-responsive aligncenter wp-image-706 " style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="http://vinsmotor-webinno.stag-innov8te.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/vmplshop-300x124.jpg" width="678" height="280" />\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="container medium-container">[WPSM_AC id=145]</div>\r\n<div class="container medium-container"></div>', '会社概要', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '481-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-10-24 10:04:01', '2016-10-24 10:04:01', '', 481, 'http://vinsmotor-webinno.stag-innov8te.com/?p=781', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
